        Q4:Please choose correct option
        <p><input type="radio" asp-for="Q4" oninput="this.className = ''" value="op21">op1</p>
        <p><input type="radio" asp-for="Q4" oninput="this.className = ''" value="op22">op2</p>
        <p><input type="radio" asp-for="Q4" oninput="this.className = ''" value="op23">op3</p>
